    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3032600/extras/705e798b2315dbe6c139a53a0b2de5b7.poster.avif?t=1722268185\" width=600 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3032600/extras/705e798b2315dbe6c139a53a0b2de5b7.webm?t=1722268185\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3032600/extras/705e798b2315dbe6c139a53a0b2de5b7.mp4?t=1722268185\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Raceborn</strong> 是一款令人振奋的赛车游戏，玩家控制微型汽车在各种充满活力的地点进行比赛。每条赛道都提供独特的挑战和展示赛车技能的机会。游戏强调创造力和定制化，允许玩家通过各种升级和改装来微调他们的车辆。随着玩家在三个不同地点和众多赛道上赢得比赛，他们会解锁新的增强功能，进一步个性化他们的汽车。Raceborn 结合了快节奏的动作和深度定制，提供了一个引人入胜和动态的赛车体验。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3032600/extras/66c4b7b4ecf18af0ee0f86cd67bbaf19.poster.avif?t=1722268185\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3032600/extras/66c4b7b4ecf18af0ee0f86cd67bbaf19.webm?t=1722268185\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3032600/extras/66c4b7b4ecf18af0ee0f86cd67bbaf19.mp4?t=1722268185\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >主要特点:</h2></strong><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >多样的赛道:</h2></strong> 在三个独特地点的各种赛道上竞争，每条赛道都有其独特的挑战。<br></li><li><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >广泛的定制:</h2></strong> 使用各种升级和改装来自定义您的微型汽车，以提高性能和风格。<br></li><li><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >进展系统:</h2></strong> 通过赢得比赛来获得升级和新部件，不断改进和个性化您的车辆。<br></li><li><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >创造性玩法:</h2></strong> 通过详细的定制选项表达您的创造力，使您的汽车真正独一无二。</li></ul>",
